### Multiple Citations

{% if citation_style.format == 'Numeric' %}
**Consecutive**: `[1-3]` or `[1, 2, 3]`

**Non-consecutive**: `[1, 5, 7]`

**Examples**:
- "Multiple studies [1-3] have confirmed..."
- "Several approaches [1, 5, 7] have been proposed..."
{% elif citation_style.format == 'Author-Year' %}
**Multiple authors**: `(Smith et al., 2024; Jones et al., 2023)`

**Same author, different years**: `(Smith et al., 2023, 2024)`

**Examples**:
- "Multiple studies (Smith et al., 2024; Jones et al., 2023) have confirmed..."
- "Several approaches (Smith et al., 2023, 2024; Lee et al., 2022) have been proposed..."
{% elif citation_style.format == 'Superscript' %}
**Consecutive**: `^1-3` or `^1,2,3`

**Non-consecutive**: `^1,5,7`

**Examples**:
- "Multiple studies^1-3 have confirmed..."
- "Several approaches^1,5,7 have been proposed..."
{% endif %}

### Citation Placement

**End of sentence**:
- "The method was validated in previous work [1]."
- "The method was validated in previous work (Smith et al., 2024)."

**Mid-sentence**:
- "As shown by Smith et al. [1], the approach is effective."
- "As shown by Smith et al. (2024), the approach is effective."

**Author as subject**:
- "Smith et al. [1] demonstrated that..."
- "Smith et al. (2024) demonstrated that..."

## Reference List Format

{% if citation_style.format == 'Numeric' %}
### Numeric Style

**Journal Article**:
```
[1] Smith, J.; Jones, A.; Lee, K. Title of the Article. Journal Name 2024, 123, 456-789.
```

**Book**:
```
[2] Author, A. Book Title; Publisher: City, Country, 2024.
```

**Book Chapter**:
```
[3] Author, A. Chapter Title. In Book Title; Editor, E., Ed.; Publisher: City, Country, 2024; pp 123-145.
```

**Conference Paper**:
```
[4] Author, A.; Author, B. Paper Title. In Proceedings of Conference Name, City, Country, Date; pp 123-130.
```

{% elif citation_style.format == 'Author-Year' %}
### Author-Year Style

**Journal Article**:
```
Smith, J., Jones, A., & Lee, K. (2024). Title of the article. Journal Name, 123, 456-789.
```

**Book**:
```
Author, A. (2024). Book title. Publisher.
```

**Book Chapter**:
```
Author, A. (2024). Chapter title. In E. Editor (Ed.), Book title (pp. 123-145). Publisher.
```

**Conference Paper**:
```
Author, A., & Author, B. (2024). Paper title. In Proceedings of Conference Name (pp. 123-130).
```

{% elif citation_style.format == 'Superscript' %}
### Superscript Style

**Journal Article**:
```
1. Smith J, Jones A, Lee K. Title of the article. Journal Name. 2024;123:456-789.
```

**Book**:
```
2. Author A. Book title. Publisher; 2024.
```

**Book Chapter**:
```
3. Author A. Chapter title. In: Editor E, editor. Book title. Publisher; 2024. p. 123-145.
```

**Conference Paper**:
```
4. Author A, Author B. Paper title. In: Proceedings of Conference Name; 2024. p. 123-130.
```

